sentences: Régis Gizavo (June 16, 1959 – July 16, 2017) was a Malagasy accordionist.
In 1990 he won the Radio France Internationale "Prix découvertes".
Gizavo partnered with Louis Mhlanga and David Mirandon to record Stories, 2006 winner of KAOS (FM)'s Spin The Globe award.
